[[=]]
+++ Water Pie
[[/=]]
[[collapsible show="+ Open Recipe" hide="by Alex Thorley"]]

Hi, today I will be showing you how to make the pie with my favorite filling, water! Water is in all of life, and in this pie too! (even though this pie is not alive). They made this pie a lot during the Great Depression but that's not why they were depressed haha, if anything this pie will cheer you right up!  That's why it's good for you. Batter up!

The first step in making this water pie is to pour one can of water in the crust. Don't worry if it gets all soggy, that's how you know it's working!

[[image https://tile.loc.gov/storage-services/service/pnp/fsa/8a28000/8a28700/8a28714r.jpg]]

Next, get your spoons out because you are going to need a lot of sugar and flour! You'll want about eight sugars for every flour, and about four of those. The resulting mixture should be dry and white.

[[image https://scp-sandbox-3.wdfiles.com/local--files/fragment%3Aartexchange2023listpages4/flour]]

Next you will put the white mixture with the water pie. 
Do *not* stir.

[[image https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/f/fb/HK_Pancake_cooking_Sept-2010_Step_003_Mixing_all_ingredients_Glutinous_Rice_Flour_with_%E8%9B%8B%E6%BC%BF_eggs_water_%E9%9B%9E%E7%B2%89_Chicken_powder.JPG/640px-HK_Pancake_cooking_Sept-2010_Step_003_Mixing_all_ingredients_Glutinous_Rice_Flour_with_%E8%9B%8B%E6%BC%BF_eggs_water_%E9%9B%9E%E7%B2%89_Chicken_powder.JPG]]

Add two small spoons of  artificial eugenol based  methyl vanillin flavoring.
DO NOT UNDER ANY CIRCUMSTANCES STIR THE MIX!!!!!!

[[image https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/b/b1/Vanillin_krist%C3%A1lyok.jpg]]

You will put butter on the pie. Preferably this butter should be made of milk from cows, but in a pinch storebought goatsuckle is fine.

[[image https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/8/8e/Bog_butter_-_Ulster_Museum.JPG]]

Put the pie in the oven.

[[image https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/8/80/Dornbirn-Ebnit-Oven-fireplace-04ASD.jpg]]

Because the pie is made of water it will be very wet when you take it out of the oven. That is okay! this is why you have spoons, to eat the water pie. Yum!

[[image https://d1ldvf68ux039x.cloudfront.net/thumbs/photos/1312/1143432/1000w_q95.jpg]]

